&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1977 indian bollywood drama film produced & directed by j. om prakash on &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; pvt ltd banner . starring reena roy , sanjeev kumar , jeetendra , sulakshana pandit in lead roles and music composed by laxmikant pyarelal . the film recorded as hit at box office . reena roy played selfish &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; that abandons her husband and child , won her numerous accolades and a filmfare award for best supporting actress . however , she rejected the award on the basis that she is the heroine of the film , not the supporting actress . this is precursor to the type of role meryl streep played two years later in " kramer vs kramer " . this film is remade in telugu as illalu ( 1981 ) starring shoban babu , sridevi , jayasudha in pivotal roles .